      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">Wix AI for HVAC Companies</h2>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-sky-50 border-[3px] border-sky-200 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">Why Wix Wins for Service Bookings</p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
